
	DataDriven Framework:-->
		Data driven framework separate test data from testcases and maintain test data in different
		spread sheets like [Propertyfiles, Excel, CsvFiles, Notepad, Json, Xml, PDf ---etc].

		

		Why datadriven is a framework:-->
			=> Because we organize different set of intput data to testcases without hardcoding it

		Advantages of DataDriven:-->
			=> Any non technical person can update data without disturbing code
			=> Redule line of code because spread sheets allow multiple set of data to drive on testcase
			=> Data Reusability , Easy to maintain, Flexible  --etc
